room_title: Escape room "KGBe Careful" by Crack the Code in Laconia
room_description: It’s 1962 and the world is gripped by the Cold War. The United States and the Soviet Union run clandestine operations across the globe. As Secret Service agents, you’ve heard chatter about a KGB plot to assassinate the first family. You’ve infiltrated a KGB hideout to investigate and neutralize the threat against the president, but things are not what they seem...
